title: Episode 25: Happy Anniversary, Paul Wiedefeld
dc:creator: Martin Di Caro
description: On this week's podcast, we talk Metro's steps toward reducing service hours, a Silver Line throwdown and Metro General Manager Paul Wiedefeld's first year on the job.
